data.description: Welcome to Hidden Springs, a quiet and tucked away neighborhood close to the top of Desert Hot Springs. Here you will find a 3 bed 3 bath home with a room which can be used as a den, study or gym! Amazing floorplan with expansive kitchen, breakfast bar as well as dining area. Large primary bedroom ensuite with dual sinks, a large tub with separate shower and walk-in closet. Oversized backyard with covered patio, great space to entertain and even build a pool! 3-car garage as well as oversized driveway. No HOAs! Call today for a private showing!
